title: SpaceX launches Starlink satellites on record 32nd flight of Falcon 9 rocket (video)
description: A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket carrying 29 Starlink satellites lifted off from NASA's Kennedy Space Center in Florida on Monday, Dec. 8, 2025. It was the record 32nd flight of the Falcon's first stage.
